sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant WOCS as WOCS Order System
    actor Operator as Warehouse Operator (Handheld)
    participant Billing as Phase 1 Billing Module

    Client->>WOCS: Submit Order (API/File/Manual)
    WOCS->>WOCS: Record Order & Apply Configured SLA Start
    WOCS-->>Client: Acknowledge (State: Received)
    WOCS->>WOCS: Check Inventory & Allocate Stock
    WOCS->>Operator: Display Order on Handheld
    
    Operator->>WOCS: Scan Barcode & Pick Item
    WOCS->>WOCS: Update State (Picked) & Log Timestamp
    
    Operator->>WOCS: Pack Item
    WOCS->>WOCS: Update State (Packed) & Log Timestamp
    
    opt SLA Warning
        WOCS->>WOCS: Check if Current Time > (SLA Deadline - 2 hours)
        WOCS-->>Operator: Display SLA Warning Alert
    end
    
    Operator->>WOCS: Dispatch Order
    WOCS->>WOCS: Update State (Dispatched) & Log Timestamp
    
    %% SLA Check
    alt Dispatch Time <= SLA Duration
        WOCS->>WOCS: Mark SLA Met
    else Dispatch Time > SLA Duration
        WOCS->>WOCS: Mark SLA Breached & Log for Reporting
    end

    %% Billing Trigger
    WOCS->>Billing: Log 'Picking' & 'Handling' Activity
    Billing->>Billing: Calculate Charge (Predefined Rate * Qty)